that's very popular among historians

00:27:59.340 --> 00:28:02.890
and academics and political
scientists in general and,

00:28:02.890 --> 00:28:04.840 position:58%
you know, talking heads in the press.

00:28:04.840 --> 00:28:08.830 position:58%
And I would just point out -- I mean,

00:28:08.830 --> 00:28:13.160
I don't have any particular
insight in that, I would venture.

00:28:13.160 --> 00:28:20.870 position:72%
But I would just point out that the end of the
