00:28:20.870 --> 00:28:27.880
to an end for about the last
40 years, ever since the 70s.

00:28:27.880 --> 00:28:30.760
And yet it continues.

00:28:30.760 --> 00:28:38.100 position:66%
We may finally with the rise of a powerful
China see things change but I think

00:28:38.100 --> 00:28:43.150 position:69%
that really has more to do with Chinese
history than American history at this point.

00:28:43.150 --> 00:28:44.980 position:58%
That would be my personal take on it.

00:28:44.980 --> 00:28:48.470
I'm not exactly sure what
Woodrow Wilson would say.

00:28:48.470 --> 00:28:54.890 position:69%
I think he would probably be very optimistic
about America's prospects for the future,

00:28:54.890 --> 00:28:57.840
as many of the American presidents

00:28:57.840 --> 00:29:02.070
from the early 20th century
were, like Theodore Roosevelt.

